{"word":"H7623 - שָׁבַח - shâbach - shaw-bakh' - Commend","slug":"H7623","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁבַח</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>shâbach"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>shaw-bakh'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Commend"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D1;&#x05D7; - sha&#x0302;bach</b> - <i>shaw-bakh'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>address</i> in a loud tone, that is, (specifically) <i>loud</i>; figuratively to <i>pacify</i> (as if by words): - commend, glory, keep in, praise, still, triumph."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3431\">H3431</a>"}]}